- That's not a color.

05:39.005 --> 05:40.840
Can you put me
in touch with him?

05:40.840 --> 05:41.799
Why?

05:41.799 --> 05:45.344
Trish Upon A Star
can totally do this.

05:45.344 --> 05:47.055
I mean, I am ready
to show them, like,

05:47.055 --> 05:49.098
10 different placemat
settings right now

05:49.098 --> 05:52.101
- that will blow their minds.
- (Joel laughs)

05:52.101 --> 05:53.603
- Joel: Uh...
- And also, this will be really,

05:53.603 --> 05:55.521
really good for my portfolio.

05:55.521 --> 05:59.150
- Trish Upon A Star
is an adorable name.
- Tricia: Oh, thank you.

05:59.150 --> 06:00.985
But how is this the first
I'm hearing about this?

06:00.985 --> 06:03.237
- Yeah, how have I never
heard about this?
- I totally told you, stop.

06:03.237 --> 06:05.865
- Well, I don't retain
information, Tricia.
- I know, that's the problem.

06:05.865 --> 06:08.951
Sam, please.
Please, please, please,
please, please, please,

06:08.951 --> 06:11.788
- I just--
- I'm begging. This is something
I really, really need.

06:11.788 --> 06:14.707
I mean, I could really...
I could really use this.

06:14.707 --> 06:16.167
Tricia, this feels like
a really bad idea.

06:16.167 --> 06:18.127
Every time I try to mix
you with my friends,

06:18.127 --> 06:19.670
- it does not go well.
- That is not even true!

06:19.670 --> 06:23.299
- And then you blame me!
- You're so drama.
Can you just not?

06:23.299 --> 06:24.383
- Please?
- It's a no from me.

06:24.383 --> 06:25.676
- Joel, back me up.
- Joel!

06:25.676 --> 06:27.970
Let's just have a meeting.
Let's just have a meeting.

06:27.970 --> 06:30.306
- Yes! When can I meet 'em?
- Why are you not backing me up?

06:30.306 --> 06:32.266
You wanna just
gimme their number?
I can just text them.

06:32.266 --> 06:34.310
- I'm not giving you
their number.
- Tricia: Thank you, Joel!

06:34.310 --> 06:36.729
- (clank)
- Thank you, Joel.

06:36.729 --> 06:39.732
Joel:
Since when is Tricia
an event designer?

06:39.732 --> 06:42.860
- She's not.
Joel, I'm trying to watch.
- (TV chattering)

06:42.860 --> 06:44.570
Oh, I'm sorry.

06:47.490 --> 06:49.784
God, her skirt is so short.

06:49.784 --> 06:51.202
Is she gonna
sleep with him?

06:51.202 --> 06:52.537
She shouldn't
sleep with him.

06:52.537 --> 06:54.122
Joel,
she already did last week,

06:54.122 --> 06:56.541
and he's very good at his job.

06:56.541 --> 06:59.836
