11:19.762 --> 11:23.391
(rumbling)

11:23.391 --> 11:24.725
(wind chimes clink)

11:24.725 --> 11:26.769
Joel:
Well, the bark
definitely looks oak,

11:26.769 --> 11:29.897
but the leaves do look
a little... maple.

11:29.897 --> 11:32.149
