wearing a necklace.

13:00.779 --> 13:02.656
- (all laugh)
- It's pretty exciting.

13:02.656 --> 13:05.117
- Fred: I'll let
you girls finish.
- Tricia: Well, anyway,

13:05.117 --> 13:06.911
