13:14.293 --> 13:16.837
Hey, how's the song coming?

13:16.837 --> 13:18.088
- It's good. Good.
- Yeah?

13:18.088 --> 13:19.924
- It's good. Good, yeah.
- Feeling it?

13:19.924 --> 13:21.467
Yeah.

13:21.467 --> 13:22.843
Feeling that
monkey's butthole, too.

13:22.843 --> 13:25.638
(giggles) This one.
She's got the eye.

13:25.638 --> 13:28.390
Oh, you're so sweet.
